description: Ukraine said it had struck the flagship of Russia’s Black Sea fleet with missiles, while Russia claimed the damage was caused by a fire. The attack on the ship came as Moscow moved to escalate its offensive in eastern and southern Ukraine, and E.U. leaders considered the oil ban despite its potential to increase energy prices around the bloc.
